Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:49.71,B2,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.71,0:01:51.69,B2,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Your power is now…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.39,0:01:56.01,B2,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,much closer to power you once possessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.55,0:02:04.39,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,“Invaders Must Die.”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:07.39,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What…is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.73,0:02:15.78,B2,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:18.94,B2,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t want me to come in contact with
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.94,0:02:21.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki when his \Npowers are still incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.06,0:02:25.70,B2,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Especially when he’s so close \Nto perfecting it. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.89,0:02:31.01,B2,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Yukio.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:39.93,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey…What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.81,0:02:43.68,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What’s going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:45.26,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Let me out of here! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.97,0:03:10.54,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,No you don’t!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.15,0:03:44.97,B2,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Save complete…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:47.02,B2,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Now…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:49.84,B2,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki, who’s close \Nto being fully developed,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.84,0:03:52.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,won’t have to come in contact with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.45,0:03:55.00,B2,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe you made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.86,0:03:58.89,B2,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn’t you have confined \Nme in there, instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:00.54,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.54,0:04:03.51,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,I didn’t have enough \Nbattery life to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:07.97,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, that wasn’t why I saved Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.92,0:04:09.83,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:10.91,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,You hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:16.05,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.41,0:04:18.86,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,We’ve attracted a crowd, the \Npolice and the fire department…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.71,0:04:22.31,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,We’ve caused violent explosions…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:25.74,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,TV news choppers might \Neven come flying by…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:31.23,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn’t that be a problem for \Nyou, as well, Mr. Tsukishima?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.11,0:04:39.30,B2,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,“The Love Gun”?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:41.60,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:43.54,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,You know what it can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.83,0:04:45.68,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,You made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.23,0:04:48.38,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Mind making yourself scarce?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:50.22,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:52.98,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,really good at these types of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:04:59.34,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,Get going, Mr. Tsukishima…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:01.86,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,But if you want to make \Na spectacle of yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.27,0:05:05.90,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,then I suggest you stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.83,0:05:22.25,B2,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:25.88,B2,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,See you again, Riruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:38.37,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,We should go, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:40.92,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll take Ichigo and Jackie with us…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:45.42,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Chad! What’s wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:46.03,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:02.87,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.98,0:06:09.22,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:11.14,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to call you here \Non such short notice…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:13.19,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:14.99,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,No…don’t mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.55,0:06:17.35,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,How’re you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:18.73,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,A lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:19.90,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,That’s good…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:21.56,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,So, what’s the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:23.32,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,About that…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:28.20,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to heal these wounds right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:29.26,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Huh…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:31.27,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, no problem, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:32.66,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Why all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:34.84,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,The situation’s changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.53,0:06:39.12,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosakii…made contact with \Nthe guy who did this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:43.75,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,His Spiritual Pressure is \Ndifferent than it was before,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:46.80,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,but it was definitely Kurosaki’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:49.81,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know why his \NSpiritual Pressure changed,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:52.52,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,but what’s certain is that I can’t \Nbide my time recovering in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:55.97,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve sensed that something’s \Ndifferent, too, haven’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.23,0:06:58.45,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I did, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:07:02.28,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,But Kurosaki hasn’t said \Nanything to me yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:05.19,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,so I’ve kept my distance…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.50,0:07:09.61,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.94,0:07:12.60,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,If the presence I sensed \Ntogether with Kurosaki
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.60,0:07:14.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,is the person who attacked you…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:16.16,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Then…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:24.96,B2,ORHIME,0000,0000,0000,,I think he’s the same \Nperson who attacked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:27.94,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:46.56,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,All right, load complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:48.69,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:50.73,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Our alternate hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:53.10,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,It’s far from comfortable, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:54.08,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:56.95,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,If you say things like that, \NI’m not adding any amenities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:08:00.57,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not your money, but all you \Ndo is complain for gosh sake…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.65,0:08:03.67,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,It’s my money that’s going to end up
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:05.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,paying to fix previous hideout…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.91,0:08:06.92,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:10.56,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,But you caused a lot of explosions…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:13.20,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,Do I spend money to fix it up the way it was,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:15.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,or rebuild from scratch?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:17.60,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,I’d better calculate which is cheaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:19.81,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Take that up with Chad…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.79,0:08:23.33,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,When he wakes up, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:29.02,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:34.66,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to be the \None who looks after him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:37.20,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Really…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:41.01,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Both Chad and Jackie’s injury are nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:44.04,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t get theatrical and \Nfaint on us like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:46.04,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,If I leave them alone, they’ll \Nwake right up, won’t they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:46.96,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,For crying out loud…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.87,0:08:51.68,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:09:01.52,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Chad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:08.26,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Chad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:10.34,B2,SADO,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:12.03,B2,SADO,0000,0000,0000,,I’m okay…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:14.15,B2,SADO,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not serious…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:17.24,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Good…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:20.70,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What about that guy, Tsukishima?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:22.78,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,He retreated…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.17,0:09:25.71,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,For now, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:28.44,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Something bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.16,0:09:30.17,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.66,0:09:33.60,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,If he wanted to hurt us,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:36.27,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,he could’ve still kept \Nfighting in that situation…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:39.53,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Especially with his power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.77,0:09:43.81,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Riruka was inside of \NTsukishima’s attack radius,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:47.35,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,and he could’ve cut down Yukio, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:49.96,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Was the reason he didn’t attack them
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.96,0:09:52.70,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,because he was actually \Nonly interested in you…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:54.90,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Or…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:57.64,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Did he have some other reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:01.62,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,You’re overthinking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:05.24,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Tsukishima knows my abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:08.34,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn’t attack me \Nunder those conditions while
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.34,0:10:10.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I had the terminal in my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.70,0:10:14.58,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,Even more so if he’s \Ninterested in Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:17.50,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose you’re right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:23.57,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Kutsuzawa, how’s your end?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.38,0:10:26.78,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,No problems at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:31.12,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,The police, fire department, \Nreporters and neighbors—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:33.48,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,they’ve all been taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:34.87,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.62,0:10:39.54,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, I’ll start \Nworking on an estimate…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:41.77,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,Man, what a headache this is going to be…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:43.45,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Yukio.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:48.04,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Stay here and work with \NIchigo on his training.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.32,0:10:49.27,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:50.75,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.97,0:10:53.54,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,There’s nothing I can do for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:56.31,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, this thing’s \Nabout to lose its charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:10:58.92,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,There is, that’s why I’m asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:00.51,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Do it with the cord plugged in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.90,0:11:03.76,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,I’m exhausted after what just \Nhappened, so I don’t want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:06.49,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,So the truth comes out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:08.89,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know how Tsukishima
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:12.71,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,found our hideout, but \Nit’d be reasonable to
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:15.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,assume he traced the Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:19.01,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,If that’s so, then your Fullbring,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:21.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,which can completely block \Noff Spiritual Pressure,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:23.41,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,will be essential to Ichigo’s training.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:26.19,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:29.96,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.20,0:11:32.81,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Training…as in an actual fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:33.71,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:36.63,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that suits you best, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.99,0:11:39.84,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, I’ve \Nalready defeated Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.53,0:11:42.22,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Who will I be fighting next?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.99,0:11:47.20,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:02.07,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Strange…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:05.53,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,You and I were attacked by the same person,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:08.15,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,but the extent of your \Ninjuries versus mine…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:12.33,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,suggests an enemy with \Ndifferent capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:14.62,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,One other thing…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:16.48,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Did you notice a sweet smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:18.05,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,A sweet smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:19.90,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,What was it now…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.48,0:12:22.30,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Honey, maybe…?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:24.51,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,I remembered something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.08,0:12:29.86,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,He called his Zanpakuto-like \Npower “Fullbring”!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:33.23,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Was it the same for the person \Nwho attacked you, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.11,0:12:35.15,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:38.82,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,I didn’t have the luxury \Nto ask questions…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:40.92,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Until you mentioned it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:44.61,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that that sword \Nwas a type of Zanpakuto…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:54.18,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Sado.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.18,0:12:55.25,B2,SADO,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.68,0:12:57.00,B2,SADO,0000,0000,0000,,If you’re taking this street…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:57.85,B2,SADO,0000,0000,0000,,Were you at the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:13:00.50,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I was there, healing \NIshida’s injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:01.49,B2,SADO,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.77,0:13:02.95,B2,SADO,0000,0000,0000,,How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.95,0:13:05.33,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,His wounds have healed,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.33,0:13:07.68,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,but I think he should stay \Nin bed a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:11.26,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,They don’t seem to be injuries caused by
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:12.87,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,ordinary Spiritual Pressure…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:16.00,B2,SADO,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.41,0:13:17.83,B2,SADO,0000,0000,0000,,I’m glad I met you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:19.94,B2,SADO,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to ask you how Ishida was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:22.06,B2,SADO,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me as we walk back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.06,0:13:22.79,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.79,0:13:24.61,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, Sado!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:25.65,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:27.74,B2,SADO,0000,0000,0000,,To where Ichigo is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:32.47,B2,SADO,0000,0000,0000,,From here on, Ichigo’s training \Nwill require your powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.57,0:13:41.32,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I’ll begin now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:01.94,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:05.65,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what I was being kept in earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:07.11,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:12.79,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,This is Yukio’s Fullbring, \N“Invaders Must Die.”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:15.51,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,He can trap a target in another dimension
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.51,0:14:18.76,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,and “control” it on a game screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:24.34,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:26.72,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve told him not to interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:31.52,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Ever fantasize about being inside a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:34.25,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.25,0:14:35.15,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.58,0:14:38.11,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Every kid’s thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.58,0:14:40.48,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing to be embarrassed about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.64,0:14:44.69,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t say I never \Nthought about it, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:45.90,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.98,0:14:49.41,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve never wanted to, not even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.63,0:14:51.55,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Then why’d you make me say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.55,0:14:55.92,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whether you did or not \Ndoesn’t make any difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:57.58,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,So why’d you make me say it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.24,0:15:02.01,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,This might be a bit different \Nthan you imagined…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:07.30,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to tell you that this is what \Nthe inside of a game looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.75,0:15:12.26,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,It’s definitely a lot more \Nbarren than I thought it’d be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:14.95,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,Barren? In that case…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:22.23,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How’s this? Isn’t it a lot livelier? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:24.75,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,It’s awfully one-dimensional, though…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:28.10,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Yukio, you don’t have to \Ndo anything unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:36.87,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, though, since you’ve \Nentered this game space,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:40.32,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,don’t you want rules fitting for a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:42.04,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.92,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing too complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:46.96,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,A simple “system.”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.39,0:15:48.33,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Yukio!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.73,0:15:50.22,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Can you give us a life gauge?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:54.00,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay. Matched to your current health? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:56.43,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,No. Make it an even six each.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.84,0:15:57.82,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.18,0:16:04.58,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.85,0:16:09.43,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,When those six life gauges are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.43,0:16:11.66,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,So it’s “game over”…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.66,0:16:13.41,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:17.03,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need an explanation \Nof “game over”?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.54,0:16:18.83,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:21.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.53,0:16:26.17,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,When it’s “game over,” \NI’ll put up a “You Die.”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.16,0:16:28.62,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Very funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:33.13,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.37,0:16:35.34,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:40.14,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,“Cross of Scaffold.”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.26,0:17:23.32,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.07,0:17:26.08,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Who’s that girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.93,0:17:28.23,B2,SADO,0000,0000,0000,,This is Inoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.51,0:17:30.70,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.70,0:17:31.82,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,She’s the one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.25,0:17:37.78,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Hello…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.44,0:17:42.27,B2,SADO,0000,0000,0000,,This is Riruka Dokugamine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:44.77,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:46.59,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Chad’s told me about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.59,0:17:49.21,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,He says you can heal people’s injuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.43,0:17:50.90,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,What’d you come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.90,0:17:53.13,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you here to help with \NIchigo’s training?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:58.01,B2,SADO,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Riruka…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:17:59.85,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:02.19,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize what you’ll be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.19,0:18:06.77,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Healing his injuries means he’s \Ngoing to get injured again later!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:12.52,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,If you heal him, Ichigo will get \Ninjured and suffer over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:16.99,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,You’re…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:20.50,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,worried for Kurosaki, too, aren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:23.27,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.27,0:18:25.78,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,No, I… I’m not!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.78,0:18:26.87,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Now just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.43,0:18:29.58,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,I realize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:31.34,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:35.55,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,I got past that issue a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:41.61,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,If Kurosaki needs my help to \Ndo what he’s decided to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.07,0:18:43.97,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,regardless of what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:47.02,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,I will use my powers to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:55.36,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,What if Ichigo suffers a terrible \Ninjury he can’t recover from?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:18:59.57,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t ever let him suffer an injury
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:02.00,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,he can’t recover from.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.42,0:19:05.90,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hopeless the injury,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:09.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will heal it completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:20.34,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He wields that huge sword as \Nthough it weighs nothing… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.76,0:19:29.00,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Coming at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.97,0:19:37.36,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve gotten quite a bit \Nbetter at wielding Fullbring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:38.82,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,But …
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:47.79,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,You still have a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:01.97,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:03.72,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.69,0:20:07.67,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,Ginjo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:08.81,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,A visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.23,0:20:10.61,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,I’m letting her in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:22.40,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if it isn’t the healing item.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:23.76,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.76,0:20:24.85,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.85,0:20:25.87,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,I’m…uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:28.17,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Skip the greetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.17,0:20:30.84,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,You’re just in time for a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.84,0:20:32.37,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and heal him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.63,0:20:35.85,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:44.49,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Come on…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:46.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:55.14,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,So that’s the last of it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.11,0:20:57.74,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about this…?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.10,0:20:59.27,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:00.54,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Get off my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.97,0:21:02.74,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do you need to make sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:07.35,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,A father may rob his son’s future.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:10.79,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s only right to confirm multiple \Ntimes that you’re certain about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:18.04,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,And I’m saying to stop \Nasking me again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.43,0:21:22.38,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you’re right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.49,0:21:28.35,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let’s move on to our last step.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.80,0:21:36.73,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Just place your Spiritual Pressure \Nin here and it’s done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.22,0:21:39.88,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, please do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.52,0:21:41.48,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:22.57,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Our next episode will \Nbe a New Years special.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.57,0:23:24.54,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, looks like it’s going to \Nbe an all-star of Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.54,0:23:25.51,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.51,0:23:27.80,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I can pretty much tell from \Nwhat we’re seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:31.52,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t really believe what’s being \Nshown is going to be everything, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.52,0:23:32.53,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What?! It’s not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.53,0:23:33.47,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,That, is a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:34.93,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,It is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.23,0:23:37.22,B2,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Xcution Dictionary!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.50,0:23:38.81,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.34,0:23:41.00,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,An extra level.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.00,0:23:41.81,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t it fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.61,0:23:44.57,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that’s a poisonous swamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.93,0:23:46.90,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me that sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.78,0:23:49.15,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.15,0:23:50.28,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.28,0:23:53.06,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,I’m at level 40 right now, so to join me,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.06,0:23:54.88,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,you’ll need to go to the castle, \Nget the secret treasure,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.88,0:23:57.75,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,and defeat the monster in the hills \Nand reach level 35 first, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.75,0:23:58.51,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.79,0:24:02.29,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,You can’t use the healing item \Nuntil you get to a higher level.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.73,0:24:04.66,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What a hassle!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.66,0:24:06.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,